{"article_id":"pLas50M6H2zgJ1MU","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"The political battle in Texas over proposed restrictions on abortion resumes on Monday with a rally by abortion opponents and a public hearing in the state Senate ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"where Democrat Wendy Davis staged a filibuster last month","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"to stall the Republican-backed measure .","depth":5},{"id":3,"text":"Davis 's tactic forced Republicans to start over in the state legislature their effort","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"to pass a ban on most abortions after 20 weeks of pregnancy","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"and toughen regulations for abortion clinics .","depth":5},{"id":6,"text":"Crowds of people","depth":4},{"id":7,"text":"advocating on both sides of the debate","depth":4},{"id":8,"text":"were expected to converge on the Texas capitol building for the public hearing in the Senate","depth":4},{"id":9,"text":"starting on Monday morning .","depth":4},{"id":10,"text":"In an exclusive * Hot Air interview , Lt . Governor David Dewhurst of Texas insists","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"that the attempt","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"to hijack the legislative process by pro-abortion activists this week","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"will not stop the state from passing a limitation on late-term abortions and requirements","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"for clinics to meet the same standards as other ambulatory surgical centers .","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"Dewhurst also says","depth":6},{"id":16,"text":"that his office is reviewing the security tapes from the demonstration","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"that derailed the bill at the end of the regular session ,","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"and that arrests may be made","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"for inciting a riot","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"- including perhaps some members of the media .","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"\" I had the votes , \"","depth":9},{"id":22,"text":"Dewhurst told me ,","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"\" I had the strategy. \"","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"He had wanted the Senate to tackle the bill , SB5 , a little earlier in the session","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"to prevent the obstructionism","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"that he foresaw .","depth":10},{"id":27,"text":"When it came time","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"to clear the galleries ,","depth":10},{"id":29,"text":"Dewhurst lacked the resources","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"to finish the job on time .","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"\" These are common sense ... measures","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"that the majority , the big majority of Texans support , \"","depth":10},{"id":33,"text":"Dewhurst insisted ,","depth":9},{"id":34,"text":"\" so I was frustrated .","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"I ' m not going to let a minority group of demonstrators","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"- Planned Parenthood and ACLU -","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"block the will of the majority .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"And I will pass this bill . \"","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"UPDATE :","depth":4},{"id":40,"text":"HB2 is on the calendar for tomorrow","depth":6},{"id":41,"text":"( Tuesday ) .","depth":6},{"id":42,"text":"SB1 , the Senate version of HB2 , is being debated in a hearing today","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"( not HB2","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"as written below )","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"and will be on the Senate floor for debate later this week.","depth":6},{"id":46,"text":"-- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- -- --","depth":3},{"id":47,"text":"The battle","depth":7},{"id":48,"text":"to ban abortions after five months","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"continues today in Texas .","depth":6},{"id":50,"text":"The Texas Senate Committee on Health and Human Services is expected to hold a hearing onSB1 Monday , a bill","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"requiring abortion clinics meet basic medical standards","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"while banning abortions after 20 weeks .","depth":9},{"id":53,"text":"The legislation is a duplicate of SB5 ,","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"which was defeated through filibuster and a rowdy protest crowd two weeks ago .","depth":8},{"id":55,"text":"Lieutenant Governor David Dewhurst made it clear last week to Hot Air 's Ed Morrissey","depth":7},{"id":56,"text":"that another disruption in the Democratic process by protestors","depth":9},{"id":57,"text":"linked to the Occupy movement","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"wo n't be tolerated.","depth":8},{"id":59,"text":"The Senate hearing is expected to start at 10 am central time","depth":5},{"id":60,"text":"and can be watched here .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":121,"left":70,"right":120,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":70,"left":66,"right":69,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":66,"left":63,"right":65,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":63,"left":0,"right":62,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":62,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":65,"left":3,"right":64,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":64,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":69,"left":67,"right":68,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":67,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":68,"left":8,"right":9,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":105,"right":119,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":105,"left":98,"right":104,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":98,"left":74,"right":97,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":74,"left":10,"right":73,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":73,"left":71,"right":72,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":71,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":72,"left":13,"right":14,"relation":"e